data.description: Welcome to 155 Saddle Drive! This home is excellently located between Sparta and Cookeville and is attractive and warm.  Plenty of curb appeal on this sided home with stone accents.  Split design with open living spaces and upgrades such as hardwood floors throughout (even in closets), custom cabinets with granite tops, master en suite with walk in shower, expansive back deck with hot tub looking out over private backyard that has a fire pit and views of neighboring fields and wildlife.  Located in a welcoming subdivision and has a paved drive and true 2 car garage.
